<p>Queries with 8 or more words are <a href="https://heroicrankings.com/seo/managed/google-ai-overview-statistics-2026/">7x more likely</a> to trigger AI Overviews. Users are asking longer, more specific questions because AI can handle them.</p>
<p>This shift changes what "ranking" even means. Visibility now includes being cited in an AI answer, not just holding position 1 in organic results.</p>
